CatDescriptText: The poster hanging in front of the ticket window reads, "Playing Nightly, Krazy Kris Columbo and His Swinging Gentlemen, Stan "the Man" Hunter on Organ, Earl Edwards, Tenor Sax, Gil Askey on Trumpet, and Floyd Smith on Guitar.  Matinees Mon & Sat 5 to 8 pm".
TitMainTitle: Ticket window with poster image of Chris Columbo and the Chris Columbo Quintette
